org.hps.conditions.run

Class RunSpreadsheet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.conditions.run.RunSpreadsheet

  • public final class RunSpreadsheet
extends Object
    A simple representation of the 2015 run spreadsheet (runs from 3/28 to 5/19) read from an exported CSV file as a list of records.

    Master copy of the spreadsheet is located at HPS_Runs_2015.

    The rows are accessible as raw CSV data through the Apache Commons CSV library, and this data must be manually cleaned up and converted to the correct data type before being inserted into the conditions database.
